Package org.dspace.services

Core DSpace service definitions.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
CachingService A service to manage creation and retrieval of caches.
ConfigurationService This service handles retrieval of the configuration data for a DSpace instance.
EventService Allows the creation of system events and registration of event listeners for notification of system events.
RequestService Allows for the managing of requests in the system in a way which is independent of any underlying system or code.
SessionService Provides access to user sessions and allows for initializing user sessions.
